    "spell": {
        "name": "All-Encompassing Hunger",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "**Sin:** gluttony  \n  \nYou reach out to devour a life, regardless of whether you need it for sustenance. The target takes 1d6 void damage, with a basic Fortitude save. If the creature is reduced to 0 Hit Points, it dies, and you gain temporary Hit Points equal to the damage dealt. These temporary Hit Points last for 1 minute.",
